---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — BBQ It Guide" description="Terms of service for the BBQ It Guide fan site. Disclaimer, data accuracy, and usage terms.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Unofficial Fan Site</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">This website is an unofficial, fan-created guide for the Roblox game BBQ It. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially connected to Roblox Corporation, the BBQ It development team, or any related entities. All game content, names, and trademarks referenced on this site are the property of their respective owners.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Data Accuracy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">All game data, values, statistics, and information presented on this site are based on community observations and are provided as estimates. In-game values may change with updates. Our calculators use estimated default values that you can edit manually. We are not responsible for decisions made based on estimated data.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Calculator Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Our calculator tools are provided for informational and entertainment purposes only. Results are estimates based on assumed game mechanics and community-reported values. Actual in-game results may vary significantly.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Third-Party Content</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">This site displays third-party advertisements through Adsterra. Ad content is managed by the ad network and is not endorsed by us. We are not responsible for the content of third-party ads.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Use of This Site</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">By using this site, you agree to use the information provided for personal, non-commercial purposes. You acknowledge that all game data is estimated and may not be accurate. If you have questions, please visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-orange-500 underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
